channel.title: Tracking and receiving the Axoloti in the U.S
channel.description: Just looking for anyone in the U.S. that has purchased and received the Axoloti and how long did it take and where are you from? I'm in California, Bay Area and ordered one of these amazing devices and although it's only been a couple of days I am already fraught with anticipation! I apologize if this isn't in the correct place.

item.title: Tracking and receiving the Axoloti in the U.S
item.dc:creator: @Phitar Darryl McGee
item.description:
@Phitar wrote:

I live on the east coast (Virginia). Ordered two on 7/19, they were processed/shipped 7/21 and I had them by 7/29 so there wasn't a long delay at all. Arrived faster than I expected.

Read full topic
